name: Obsidian Package
description:
In this Obsidian donator package, you will receive the following!

- Legendary Donator status.
- Your own personal memorial at spawn
- 20 Stacks of Cobblestone
- 2 stacks of cooked Steak
- 2 stacks of cooked pork
- 50 obsidian
- 150 wood logs
- 100 wood planks
- 80 iron ingots
- 25 diamonds
- Full set of Diamond Tools and Armour.
-$150,000 in game money
